schools.name: Thomas W Holtzman Jr  El School

data.description: This 3BR, 2.5 bath townhome in Saddle Ridge at Waverly offers a convenient & accessible location, making it a great choice for those looking to live near Downtown Harrisburg and the Riverfront with easy access to major routes like I-81 & Rt. 322.  An added benefit is the carefree living that you will enjoy as the condo association takes care of the outdoor maintenance of the condo as well as lawn and snow removal.  There is also use of the fitness center included in your monthly dues.  As the seasons change, you will love the spectacular mountain view that provides a beautiful background to the community.  Key features & highlights of this home include main level laundry, hardwood flooring in hallway & dining area, vaulted primary bedroom with attached bath & walk-in closets in all 3 bedrooms.  The kitchen features a breakfast bar which opens to the dining area.  There is access to the back patio for outdoor enjoyment  & includes an attached shed.  Selling "as is"  Home Inspection Report available for review.
